---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="문서">
  <div class="docs-container">
    <h1>문서</h1>
    <p class="subtitle">Sudoremove의 AI 교육 자료와 튜토리얼</p>
    
    <section class="docs-section">
      <h2>Physical AI</h2>
      <div class="docs-grid">
        <a href="/docs/physical-ai/getting-started" class="doc-card">
          <h3>시작하기</h3>
          <p>HuggingFace LeRobot을 활용한 Physical AI 입문</p>
        </a>
        <a href="/docs/physical-ai/tutorial" class="doc-card">
          <h3>튜토리얼</h3>
          <p>단계별 실습 가이드</p>
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="docs-section">
      <h2>LLM 강의 아카이브</h2>
      <div class="docs-grid">
        <a href="/docs/llm/basics" class="doc-card">
          <h3>LLM 기초</h3>
          <p>대규모 언어 모델의 기본 개념</p>
        </a>
        <a href="/docs/llm/advanced" class="doc-card">
          <h3>고급 주제</h3>
          <p>파인튜닝과 프롬프트 엔지니어링</p>
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  .docs-container {
    max-width: 1000px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  h1 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .subtitle {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    color: #999;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .docs-section {
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .docs-section h2 {
    color: var(--accent-color);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .docs-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(280px, 1fr));
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }

  .doc-card {
    background: var(--secondary-color);
    padding: 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 0.5rem;
    text-decoration: none;
    color: var(--text-color);
    transition: transform 0.3s, box-shadow 0.3s;
    border: 1px solid transparent;
  }

  .doc-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(233, 69, 96, 0.2);
    border-color: var(--accent-color);
  }

  .doc-card h3 {
    color: var(--accent-color);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .doc-card p {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: #ccc;
  }
</style>